Say '''Tigaon''' et kumatlo ya klase baley ed luyag na [[Camarines Sur]], [[Pilipinas]]. Unong ed 2010 Census, say papulasyon to et 48,611 totoo. Walay kabaleg tan sukat to ya 72.35 sq. km. Sikato et walad kumapat ya distrito. Say zip code to et 4420.	
															
